name: orthoinspector_1.30_blast_threshold_10-9-.154.rels
description: Output data set (predicted orthologous groups) for orthoinspector 1.30 (blast threshold 10-9) tool in OrthoXML format. These orthologs were computed using the following Reciprocal Smallest Distance (RSD) parameters: divergence=0.8 and evalue=1e-5. Orthology relationships are stored in OrthoXML format
